-- Russian Court Annuls TeliaSonera, Alfa Deal on Turkcell, MegaFon, RIA Says
-- B y   A n a s t a s i a   U s t i n o v a
-- 2010-10-14T08:38:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/russian-court-annuls-teliasonera-alfa-deal-on-turkcell-megafon-ria-says.html
A Russian court struck down an
agreement between Alfa Group and TeliaSonera AB to unite their
holdings in OAO MegaFon and Turkcell Iletisim Hizmetleri AS, RIA
Novosti reported today.  TeliaSonera and billionaire Mikhail Fridman’s Alfa Group
last year agreed to combine their stakes in MegaFon, Russia’s
third-largest mobile-phone company, and Turkey’s biggest
cellular provider to create a new company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anastasia Ustinova in St. Petersburg at 
 austinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
